text: Galiakhmerovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Amangildinsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 124 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 67 km from Uchaly, 7 km from Malokazakkulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Galiakhmerovo
